com.joliciel.talismane.tokeniser

Class TaggedToken<T extends TokenTag>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.joliciel.talismane.tokeniser.TaggedToken<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the TokenTag used to tag this token.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    TokenWrapper, java.lang.Comparable<TaggedToken<T>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PosTaggedToken

    public class TaggedToken<T extends TokenTag>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<TaggedToken<T>>, TokenWrapper
    A token together with a piece of information that is tagged onto it. This can either be a tokeniser decision (whether or not this token is attached to the previous/next token) or a PosTag, or any other piece of information added by the learners.
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli
